{"tid":482636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遵理改名上市 林溢欣3年袋1.1億 勁過公司盈利","createTime":"2017-11-28T10:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T01:32:57.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d4bf96c79722f6cfea3596cf986cffff3dad3d65","tid":482636,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:54:45.000Z","msg":"早年市場傳出遵理學校計劃上市，但一直只聞樓梯響，今年遵理改名為「精英匯集團」再戰上市！據初步招股文件披露，其中一名老師3年勁袋1.14億元，比公司期間的總盈利還要多。市場盛傳該位「頂級名師」正是遵理中文科補習名師林溢欣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/YY-LAM-704-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2FYY-LAM-704-1.jpg&h=43bef325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文件顯示，遵理於2015至2017三個財政年度收入分別為3.28億、3.76億及3.76億元，公司三年都錄得盈利3,077萬、3,055萬及3,482萬元，合共9,614萬元。<br />\n<br />\n當中在「頂級名師課程及產品的收入」中，過去三年佔公司31%至40.5%收入，該名「頂級名師」過往三年的酬金分別為3,540萬、3,360萬及4,400萬元，比公司累積的三年盈利還要高，雖然文件未提及該名老師的名字，當相信就是中文科補習名師林溢欣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/%E9%81%B5%E7%90%86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2F%25E9%2581%25B5%25E7%2590%2586.jpg&h=dd96fded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">遵理各科補習導師。</span><br />\n<br />\n公司在過去三年為「五大名師」提供的薪酬總額為5,460萬、6,040萬及6,790萬元。該五大名師提供的課程及產品收入，佔集團總收入的六成，五人的合約將在2020至2021年屆滿。<br />\n<br />\n另外，文件亦披露，國際關係學者沈旭暉於2015年7月，收購遵理旗下全資附屬公司環城發展集團三成股權，目前沈旭暉同樣是公司的非執行董事，年薪近50萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/20171128_CR_-%E9%81%B5%E7%90%86%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2F20171128_CR_-%25E9%2581%25B5%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1_.jpg&h=02d885b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n集團表示，是次集資將會用作未來兩至三年內開設或優化14間教學中心，同時亦會用作招聘非教學及升級叫學中心設施、市場推廣活動及一搬營運資金用途。<br />\n<br />\n遵理學校曾計劃於2015年上市，翌年林溢欣曾被現代教育公開登報「挖過檔」，引起教育界迴響。林溢欣畢業於可風中學，2006年取得中文、中國文學、中國歷史的三優成績入讀中大中文系，並取得一級榮譽畢業後，再攻讀碩士畢業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/11/20171128_CR_-%E9%81%B5%E7%90%86%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1_%E6%A2%81%E8%B3%80%E7%90%AA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F11%2F20171128_CR_-%25E9%2581%25B5%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1_%25E6%25A2%2581%25E8%25B3%2580%25E7%2590%25AA.jpg&h=f6a235be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">遵理學校創辦人梁賀琪。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2624683-遵理改名再上市-傳林溢欣三年穩袋1-14億\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2624683-%E9%81%B5%E7%90%86%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-%E5%82%B3%E6%9E%97%E6%BA%A2%E6%AC%A3%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4%E7%A9%A9%E8%A2%8B1-14%E5%84%84&d=%2BUhygSBzZLCudYLKhSgcVAIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=5a4a3bd0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2624683-遵理改名再上市-傳林溢欣三年穩袋1-14億</a>"},{"pid":"41b6d8f0a146c84631c60bbfa5274e2cd17b321e","tid":482636,"uid":28366,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/185706_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F28%2F185706_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=067d60ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"764f5e13ba29002e14e2a92342880934de1fd0a0","tid":482636,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/28/190417_ed1e7945d9840c359714439145db20dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F